Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:18.40,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:29.86,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:36.79,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:47.92,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:56.85,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:08.74,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:20.63,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:26.47,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:36.27,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:29.86,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:36.79,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:47.92,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:56.85,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:08.74,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:20.63,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:26.47,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:36.27,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:47.33,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(100,270)}Ep. 50 - Towards the Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:06.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to see you here, Lucy.\NYou're having this day to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:06.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:08.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just great.\NMy wife would be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:14.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone doing well at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:16.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Princeton.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:17.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:20.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:24.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please make me your child!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:25.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:28.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please make me the daughter of your family!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:29.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:37.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Make me... Make me your family's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:53.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:55.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did Lucy come?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:58.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:08.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Lucy, it's so good you came! Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NWhy are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:23.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did something hurt you, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:26.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The matter with Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:30.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy came to tell us\Nthat she wants to become our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:31.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:38.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Lucy.\NYou're welcome to live with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:43.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My! What's wrong, Lucy?\NCome live with us, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:45.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment, Sylvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:51.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy came to tell us that she wants to become\Nthe daughter of our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:52.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:53.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:57.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think Lucy is lying to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:57.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:04:03.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really a desire to become our children\Nthat is driving Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:04.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:10.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,While having such wonderful\Nfather and mother of her own,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:15.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason why she would\Nsincerely want to become our child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:16.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I sincerely...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:20.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already, Lucy.\NDon't force yourself to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:25.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But tell me, why?\NWhy would Lucy say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:27.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:28.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, I'm a little curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:35.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Your father and mother at home probably\Ndon't know about you coming here, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:39.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was... It was my own idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, Lucy, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I know there was some special reason for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:49.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here, blow your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:53.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:05:03.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Lucy. Both me and Sylvia would be infinitely\Nhappy to have you as our own child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:07.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But, please understand, Lucy.\NWe gave up on that hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:11.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, can you please explain,\Nwhy is Lucy saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:20.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When I visited the Popples' house the other day\Nto put forward an offer of us adopting Lucy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:23.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy happened to be in the next room\Nand overheard everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:27.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact,\Nif you agree to us adopting Lucy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:33.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I should give you something in return,\Nlike a piece of land in my possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:35.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Land?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:36.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:40.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If I may, Mr. Popple, what is it\Nyou currently covet the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:43.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it owning your own piece of land?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A land?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:52.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd appreciate it if I hand over a part of the farm near Gawler that you agreed to work at.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:55.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:57.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it because only by becoming our daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,you could fulfill your father's dream\Nof owning his own land?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:04.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thoughts like that were what brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:13.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Mr. Princeton! I'd really\Nrather stay here with you. In exchange...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:14.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:18.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I feel... I feel so sorry for my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He had lost all hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:23.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He's no longer the dad he used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:26.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now he just drinks all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:28.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:37.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It took a while, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I took one too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:56.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom's face screams exasperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:59.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:02.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad is no longer the dad he used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:11.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't he return to how he used to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:15.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You should understand that much yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's the land, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:22.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A vast, vast wheat field,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:29.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,where dad, mom, and Ben, as well as John and Clara -\Neveryone is working together to harvest it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:33.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We've had a bumper crop this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:38.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You, me, and even Tob are bundling\Nthe harvested wheat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is working themselves into a sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The work is hard, but also fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:46.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A grasshopper stops in front of Little's nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:50.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little is awfully scared\Nand starts running around and howling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:52.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone laughs heartily at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:01.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's how we imagined things would be one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:02.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But we gave up on it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:06.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So I take refuge in seeing happy dreams, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I understand exactly how you feel, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:15.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for all the trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:18.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:23.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's us two who are at fault for even wanting\Nto separate you from such a loving family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:31.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much we adore you, going there\Nand saying we want to adopt you was unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:33.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sylvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:37.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, please escort Lucy home, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:38.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:52.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, Lucy. You can't lose your hope.\NNo matter how hard it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:53.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:56.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Something good will happen to you.\NIt won't take too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:58.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:08:58.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:00.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:04.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, it'll happen today already, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:09.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well. Goodbye, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:13.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure something good will happen to you, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get scolded if I come home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:33.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine, since you didn't tell anyone\Nyou were going to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:35.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain well all the reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:39.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean.\NI'll be scolded for not going to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:40.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:45.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,On my way to school, I split with my brother Tob\Nand went to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:48.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then we're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:51.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for today, you've no choice\Nbut to let mom scold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:57.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I needed to have an important discussion with them, so it was fortunate that you showed up. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:13.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Skipping the school and going to play around\Nat Mr. Princeton's house again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:19.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Madam, Lucy didn't come to play around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:22.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But then, what for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:27.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, she came to say\Nthat she wants me to adopt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:28.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:31.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:36.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, I beg you not to scold Lucy for this one matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:39.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, joking about such things...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:41.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, she meant it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My. But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:46.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She tried to make it seem as if she meant it,\Nbut deep inside, she knew it was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:51.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What I mean is, she wasn't sincere when saying she wants to become the daughter of our family,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:53.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,but for some other reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:57.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Which is out of consideration\Nfor the happiness of her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:59.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't quite understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:04.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I know! So that's what this all is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:05.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it about, Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:10.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy wanted to present our family with the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:13.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Exactly so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:15.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I deducted too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:21.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it was all too unbelievable that Lucy\Nwould sincerely want to become our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, so that's what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:33.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I am so, so sorry.\NWe just keep giving you more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:36.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was no trouble at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:41.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, both me and my wife\Nwere deeply moved by Lucy's dedication.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:47.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She wished for the collective happiness of the family\Neven at the cost of her own comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:53.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, I'd like you\Nto pass a certain message to your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:54.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:58.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There's a farm I own near the city of Gawler.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:00.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:05.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Part of that farm's land is still waiting to be developed.\NThere's not much of it, but still.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:09.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'd like you to pass to your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:15.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm determined to sell that land to Mr. Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:21.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because I want to see it with my own eyes -\Nhim making a fresh start in life on his wonderful farm. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:25.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Princeton...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:28.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm infinitely grateful for the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:31.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure my husband\Nwould also be most delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:35.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But well... Unfortunately, our family\Nis currently struggling with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:39.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So... We can't really afford also buying that land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And so, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:49.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, this land near Gawler also comes with a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:53.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If your whole family moves there,\Nyou will no longer need this house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:54.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:58.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sell this house to me. And then,\Nwe'll call this house a down payment for the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:04.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As for the rest, it'd be all fine with me\Nif your husband helped out on my farm in his free time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:07.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,and thus gradually worked off the cost of the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:11.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Princeton...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:16.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I hope to hear your husband's response tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:18.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Go there! Marsh, go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:31.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? He's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:33.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He's back! Dad is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad returned already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:40.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He returned, alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:43.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he didn't stop by the bar today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:45.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He's back early, so he probably didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine how dad will react?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Will be the happiest ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:51.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You dunce, saying it out loud is no fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:52.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Think he'll laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose. He'll probably laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:15:01.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, I don't ever hear\Ndad laughing sincerely and heartily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:02.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna be the one who tells him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:05.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Mom said she'll do it, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:08.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't wait to see dad's delighted face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:13.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:18.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, dad looks mighty surprised already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:21.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:24.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NAll three went out to meet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're back early today, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, something good will probably happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Something {\i1}very{\i0} good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:37.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?\NDid your mom prepare some delicious dinner today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:40.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! It's not food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:42.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What else could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:46.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Little, you know it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:51.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you {\i1}do{\i0} know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:53.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then... I really wonder what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Comment: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:54.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:55.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:56.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:09.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Princeton said he's determined to sell it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:14.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? He knows perfectly well I'm penniless,\Nand still tries to sell me something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's the land, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:20.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He wants you to buy some of his land in Gawler.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:26.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Can't you put two and two together?\NWe're as poor as a church mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We have the money for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:29.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:34.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We can sell this house. And then use this money\Nas a down payment for the land and the house there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:36.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But what's next?\NHow am I supposed to pay out the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:40.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,By working on Mr. Princeton's farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:45.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, work on our own farm comes first,\Nbut in the spare time you could help out on his farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:47.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And he'll count that money towards your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:51.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have plenty of helping hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:53.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,John and Clara, Ben too -
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:57.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,he'll quit his job at the customs office\Nto live and work with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:02.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not dreaming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:04.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:08.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Will I finally get to own my own piece of land?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:11.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. This time, nothing will stand in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:14.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Princeton is the man you can put your trust in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.99,0:17:26.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You guys all knew that, but kept silent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:29.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,See? Didn't we tell you\Nsomething very good will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:31.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:34.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All of this is happening to us thanks to Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:39.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:42.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think Mr. Princeton\Nis the one you should be thanking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:44.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly. I'll do it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:47.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But really, aren't you glad, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:52.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:53.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:55.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy, with all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:18:00.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It feels really strange. Tears are coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:05.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:08.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:19.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, Little is following us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you following us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:37.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you not to follow us\Nbecause it's such a long way to the Gawler farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, you can let him in. I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:48.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown increasingly disobedient these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:56.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Princeton took dad on a tour\Nthrough the land that's about to become his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:19:01.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He'll have to go on several more trips\Nbefore the whole family could move there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:04.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But for the first one, only Lucy could accompany him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:35.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see three eucalyptus trees\Nall the way out there in the distance? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:39.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Your plot starts from this fence\Nand only ends there, Mr. Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:51.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My plot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:57.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to seeing you make a fresh start here,\Non wonderful farm of your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:03.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can promise to you, it'll be gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:08.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see two small houses over there. \NIs that where we'll be living?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:10.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:14.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We could probably let John and Clara\Nlive in the one that's smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:14.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:37.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You wait for me here.\NI'll go introduce myself to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:38.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So many sheep they're keeping here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:04.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:06.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:12.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're not thinking of attacking these sheep, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:13.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:15.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:19.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:21.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait I said, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:45.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Snowflake! You're Snowflake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:55.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So Snowflake was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:59.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do what I can to buy her back for you, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:10.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We finished packing the bags and were finally\Nabout to depart, when it suddenly started raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:22.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It'll stop soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:24.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's a passing rain, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:28.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Even so, that's pretty unfortunate.\NOur things would get all sodden.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:50.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, setting out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.93,0:22:52.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Setting out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:58.40,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,...To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.40,0:23:09.27,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:18.20,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.48,0:23:30.09,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.37,0:23:41.98,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.26,0:23:47.82,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.10,0:23:57.62,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:08.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We set out towards the land of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:16.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,On one autumn day, some four and a half years\Nafter our arrival to Southern Australia. 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:18.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, look, a rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:21.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. It sure is pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.69,0:23:31.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like our destination\Nis exactly where that rainbow bridge starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:36.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose. One day, we'll cross\Nthat rainbow bridge for sure.
