Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.09,0:24:06.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because John stole the paper knife\Nthat Lucien had made,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.69,0:24:09.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Annette gets into a big fight with the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:12.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The new show: "The Alps Story: My Annette".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.62,0:24:14.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Episode one: "Annette and Lucien."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.88,0:24:16.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
